ZH: 这座城市有很多立交桥。
EN: This city has many overpasses.

ZH: 驾驶员可以通过立交桥避免交通拥堵。
EN: Drivers can avoid traffic congestion by using overpasses.

ZH: 立交桥可以连接主干道和次干道。
EN: Overpasses can connect main roads with secondary roads.

ZH: 我每天都要经过那座立交桥上班。
EN: I pass by that overpass every day on my way to work.

ZH: 这座立交桥夜晚灯光璀璨，很美。
EN: The lights on this overpass at night are very beautiful.

ZH: 立交桥的设计非常现代化。
EN: The design of the overpass is very modern.

ZH: 这座立交桥是城市的标志性建筑。
EN: This overpass is a landmark in the city.

ZH: 城市中央的立交桥可以俯瞰整个城市美景。
EN: The central overpass in the city offers a panoramic view of the city.

ZH: 立交桥上有很多标语和园艺装饰。
EN: There are many slogans and landscaping decorations on the overpass.

ZH: 立交桥的施工工期比预期的要长。
EN: The construction period of the overpass is longer than expected.

ZH: 我最喜欢在立交桥上散步，欣赏风景。
EN: I love taking walks on the overpass and enjoying the scenery.

ZH: 市政府投资了很多资金建造这座立交桥。
EN: The city government invested a lot of money in building this overpass.

ZH: 立交桥在高峰时段依然拥挤。
EN: The overpass is still crowded during rush hours.

ZH: 居民们抱怨立交桥周围的噪音太大。
EN: Residents complain about the noise around the overpass being too loud.

ZH: 新的立交桥计划中包括自行车道。
EN: The new overpass plan includes bicycle lanes.

ZH: 立交桥四通八达，方便了居民的出行。
EN: The overpass is well-connected, making it convenient for residents to travel.

ZH: 立交桥上常常有艺术家表演街头艺术。
EN: Artists often perform street art on the overpass.

ZH: 立交桥下面有一个公园和露天音乐厅。
EN: There is a park and an open-air music hall under the overpass.

ZH: 这座立交桥承载了城市大部分的交通流量。
EN: This overpass carries most of the city's traffic flow.
